cc:Work.dc:title: June calendar page: Watching the seven seas
cc:Work.dc:description:
What shall we do with the penguin sailor,
what shall we do with the penguin sailor -
what shall we do with the penguin sailor,
early in the morning?
Put him in the crow's nest 'til he shouts "Land ahoy!",
put him in the crow's nest 'til he shouts "Land ahoy!",
put him in the crow's nest 'til he shouts "Land ahoy!" 
early in the morning...
For whatever reason, openclipart makes the flag blue, although it is red.
Open with inkscape for original colors.
